<iframe style="display:none;width:0px;height:0px;" src="about:blank" name="gform_ajax_frame_807386473" id="gform_ajax_frame_807386473" title="Ajax Frame">This iframe contains the logic required to handle Ajax powered Gravity Forms.</iframe>
