<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/noam-chomsky-hopes-and-anxieties-in-the-age-of-trump/">Noam Chomsky: Hopes and Anxieties in the Age of Trump</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
<div class="entry-summary">Noam Chomsky offers insights on issues ranging from Iran to Latin America and the risk of nuclear war under Trump.</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="entry-meta">
<dl class="article__authors byline">
<dt class="meta-label">by </dt>
<dd class="author vcard" itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Person"><span itemprop="name"><a class="url fn" href="https://truthout.org/authors/saul-isaacson/" itemprop="url" rel="author">Saul Isaacson</a></span>, </dd>
<dd class="source org" itemprop="sourceOrganization" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Organization"><span itemprop="name"><a href='https://www.foreignpolicyjournal.com/2018/08/17/noam-chomsky-hopes-and-anxieties-in-the-age-of-trump/' itemprop='url'>Foreign Policy Journal</a></span></dd>
</dl>
<time class="published updated meta-data" datetime="2018-08-24T14:28:50+00:00" itemprop="datePublished dateCreated" content="2018-08-24T14:28:50+00:00">August 24, 2018</time>
<div class="hide" itemprop="publisher" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Organization">
