<article class="row hentry post-251861 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-interview tag-2018-midterms tag-abortion tag-climate-change tag-democratic-socialism tag-democrats tag-money-in-politics tag-nuclear-war tag-republicans section-politics-and-elections primary_topic-politics" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/NewsArticle">
<div class="small-12 medium-4 columns">
<a class="archive-image" href="https://truthout.org/articles/noam-chomsky-on-fascism-showmanship-and-democrats-hypocrisy-in-the-trump-era/" title="Noam Chomsky on Fascism, Showmanship and Democrats&#8217; Hypocrisy in the Trump Era">
<img width="400" height="300" src="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/5599576288_0927cfbf2b_o-400x300.jpg" class="attachment-sd_medium size-sd_medium" alt="" loading="lazy" srcset="https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/5599576288_0927cfbf2b_o-400x300.jpg 400w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/5599576288_0927cfbf2b_o-200x150.jpg 200w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/5599576288_0927cfbf2b_o-800x600.jpg 800w, https://truthout.org/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/5599576288_0927cfbf2b_o-1200x900.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" />
</a>
</div>
<div class="small-12 medium-8 columns archive-text">
<div class="before-headline">
<div class='sections'>
<a href='https://truthout.org/section/politics-and-elections/' rel='section' class='politics-and-elections' style='color: #1958aa;'>Politics &amp; Elections</a>
</div>
</div>
<div class="">
<h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
<a href="https://truthout.org/articles/noam-chomsky-on-fascism-showmanship-and-democrats-hypocrisy-in-the-trump-era/">Noam Chomsky on Fascism, Showmanship and Democrats&#8217; Hypocrisy in the Trump Era</a>
</h2>
</div>
<div class="entry-summary" itemprop="description">
<div>
